{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't want to be associated with me or-- or even acknowledge that this little urchin who was weeping over fresh fruit, in any shape, form, or fashion, belonged to him.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because it was an embarrassment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was my introduction to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I could not speak one word of English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't even know yes and no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And once again, had to start way, way at the bottom, at the beginning, for another language, my fourth language at this point in my 12 and a half years.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was difficult coming to this-- this town which was called Whitestone, which was beyond Flushing, New York, because it was a-- a small Yankee town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't believe they had any notion whatsoever about the war in Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They complained a lot about no coffee and silk stockings, which was rather unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I couldn't imagine how anybody could get so excited about no coffee and no silk stockings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in general, I don't believe there were any Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They had no knowledge of refugees or what refugees had gone through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In fact, I think, since the United States was not in the war, they felt this-- this was something far away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they really did not know a great deal about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was a fish out of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no one I could talk to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nobody who was understanding or sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, here I was in a very strange situation, more than happy to be alive but thoroughly confused.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
